a (web) render for https://sketchpad.keycurriculum.com/

cargo run ./path/to/your.gsp
cargo run ./path/to/one.gsp ./path/to/two.gsp

Open the generated html and click `Debug` to inspect the extracted hierarchy as a graph or raw JSON.

Each compile also writes `*.debug.json` with the payload-derived scene/debug data.

check the `.log` file to see the current missing impl and parsed steps.
